Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在你眼前  有著無限的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底兩萬哩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭懦弱的人  無法背叛藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在作夢之前  我想翱翔天際
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的音樂盒開啟  發出聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點一滴演奏出幸福與勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:01:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在你眼前  有著無限的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言語是永遠的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't  forget  to  try  in  mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛比寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時值西元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與萬能潛水艇鸚鵡螺號告別後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.81,0:01:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強、娜蒂亞與大王\N搭乘飛機來到島嶼上空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.12,0:01:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻突然遭到不名人士攻擊\N而迫降於森林之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強他們在那裡認識了\N住在島上的小女孩,瑪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉的雙親\N已遭神秘組織殺害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛蘭迪絲三人組\N也被那個組織抓了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強他們雖然也遭到攻擊\N但總算是逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:01:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔天早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強與娜蒂亞\N將瑪莉雙親的死訊告訴了她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但瑪莉卻不懂那所代表的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人也下定決心\N要保護這名小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#06  孤島要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉的家旁邊\N有一間很大的教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在這一帶嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個星期天我都會跟爸爸媽媽\N一起去祈禱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎,瑪莉真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:03:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教堂的位置大致吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人型戰車在拉著車?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,是車子在操縱人型戰車嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新亞特蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新亞特蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩們尚未出現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子要留活口,知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好,回去你的崗位\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩們?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是在找我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子要留活口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指的應該是娜蒂亞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是港口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方在上…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那條就是瑪莉說的路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,港口?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,有很多船停靠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我知道喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從教堂旁邊的路直直走\N就能看到很多船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸常帶我去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒備還真森嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本溜不進去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好驚人的貨物量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡頭會是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這裡的電量也好驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴黎也沒亮成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從哪裡輸送來的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著山裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座山裡會有什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-晚安之吻\N-吻?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不曉得嗎?\N媽媽都會親我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.93,0:06:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好睡吧,瑪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽都是說"晚安,瑪莉"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安,瑪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論村裡還是港口\N全都是那群傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是向人求助…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上哪找人幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們全都是殺人兇手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還有沒被他們發現\N躲了起來的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就跟那些人一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你告訴我那些人在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛,就會胡扯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳要我怎麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該要想個更…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是在夫妻吵架嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-才不是呢\N-才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉,對不起\N不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的,妳別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之,靠我們兩個\N根本逃不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上還有個瑪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能讓瑪莉遇上危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:08:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地的中心應該就在\N島嶼中央的露天礦坑裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了晚上我會再去查探情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以跑出去\N會有危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的花園
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以,強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛入對方基地太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想被抓住的人\N應該都被關在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們對這座島的認識
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有問瑪莉而畫出來的\N這張地圖而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須潛入基地\N取得更多情報才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經想好潛進去\N也不會被發現的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不去冒這個險\N是無法離開這座島嶼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃色的,白色的,紅色的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮吧,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要為牧克做一條\N天堂最美的項圈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫妳摘吧,小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-瑪莉…\N-別去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是現在去了\N大家都會被抓住的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:10:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們正在等\N看有沒有人會去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奸詐的一群傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒有其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回基地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,全員準備出發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-走吧,娜蒂亞\N-嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉,妳等著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會去救妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看到煙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密基地應該就在那下頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉與大王就在那裡是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把他們救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是利用以前的坑道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好亮的燈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼時候發明的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我跟鸚鵡螺號借來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條輸電線路\N應該會通到他們的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據瑪莉所說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有間大發電廠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這裡頭有許多電囉?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個帶有相當強大的電壓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便亂碰會被燒成焦炭的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是出口嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到他們的大本營了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-小心點\N-嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都是島上的人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強,你看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是湖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個就是秘密基地?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八成是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個就是火力發電廠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多煙囪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中央的塔會是什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來又不像天線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃閃發著光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是座玻璃塔嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼用途呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一頭的那個是城堡嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,這地方還真驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密密麻麻都是管子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼的工廠呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強,你什麼都不曉得嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得再到下面去調查才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是輸送帶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要輸送什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹不下去了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛蘭迪絲小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來她在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,那邊的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在做什麼\N還不快點幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別在那邊嘮嘮叨叨的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己過來挖如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然逼我這種\N嬌弱的少女做苦工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為男人你知不知羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混帳…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不費吹灰之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還挺行的嘛\N讓我刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快進入\N20世紀的科學時代了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種苦工實在跟不上潮流
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西先借我用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就快點開溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦,怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你們那麼討厭工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就帶你們去個好地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要邀請我們參加晚餐會嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以,會場就在地下監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫你們舉辦\N不吃不喝的盛大派對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-把人帶下去\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是淑女耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能對我客氣點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢蛋,給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,這條輸送帶停住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓它停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從這種地方下去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走在上頭會被發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要沿著這些管子\N到城堡去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會弄得渾身都是泥巴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊,又不是來野餐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也對,這是為了瑪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停…停下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死我了\N怎麼突然就動了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強,你看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那隻海中怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那果然是潛水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它將我爸爸的船…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人走出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新亞特蘭…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是什麼人?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地位似乎很高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新亞特蘭…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候您的大駕,石像鬼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那名女孩捉到了嗎?\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經掌握人質\N很快就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論使出怎樣的手段都無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一定要活捉她\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織規模似乎相當龐大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新亞特蘭?\N會是什麼意思呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是熔礦爐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜…娜蒂亞,下面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃到下面去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去會粉身碎骨的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住我,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造山銅調整得如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比預定遲了0.01%
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是來得及在實驗前完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一到外頭馬上會被發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但萬一要是掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會連渣都不剩的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.81,0:19:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣嚇我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是將石英熔化\N做成玻璃磚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要做什麼用呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就只會想那些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當現代化的自動工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡頭沒半個工人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻有看守的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜裡看守的人應該會少一些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時再…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時再躲到那邊的輸送帶下面\N慢慢前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照以上所言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此人造山銅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃集合我們目前所有科學力量\N所得到的結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就理論上而言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它應該能展現\N如同預料之中的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光有理論只是紙上談兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須實際用得上才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得\N這還是第一次這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前並未出現類似情況
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去調查
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是在對什麼東西產生反應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞的"蔚藍之水"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊,動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.89,0:21:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點,往這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強,光芒消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不停下來就要開槍了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.08,0:22:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊,只是擦傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你們在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經被團團包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高舉雙手乖乖出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.26,0:22:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.17,0:22:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強,那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像可以通到其它地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.01,0:22:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去之後\N你就拿著這個逃到那個洞裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.78,0:22:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只數到五
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.42,0:22:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我出去,妳就趁機…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.86,0:22:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙要抓的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.66,0:22:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:22:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.70,0:23:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我一定會回來救妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.21,0:23:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.98,0:23:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著,別開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那名女孩,要抓活的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追,別讓她逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-從右方包抄\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.01,0:23:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓她跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.22,0:23:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.32,0:23:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(待續)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.96,0:24:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼應付心中的焦急才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要看不清遠方的夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.17,0:24:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喃喃自語  仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.57,0:24:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你的約定耀眼閃爍著
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.45,0:24:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try  安慰的話語\N是傳達不到內心的風
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.59,0:24:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然背負的不安逐漸膨脹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.37,0:24:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是我自己的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.67,0:24:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人應該也不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.34,0:24:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使跌倒或感到迷惘\N仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.16,0:25:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞,我一點都不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.87,0:25:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.47,0:25:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強…強一定會來救我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.27,0:25:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.58,0:25:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石像鬼為什麼會稱呼我為公主?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.05,0:25:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.25,0:25:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底兩萬哩  下一回\N「巴別塔」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.82,0:25:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
